data.name: textStartFolder.ToolTip
data.value: Specify here the folder from which the folder walk will start. The importer will browse the folder tree in alphabetical order, from the Start Folder until the End Folder is reached. One word document will be created and saved for each folder browsed.

data.name: textEndFolder.ToolTip
data.value: Specify here the folder at which the folder walk will end. The importer will browse the folder tree in alphabetical order, from the Start Folder until the End Folder is reached. One word document will be created and saved for each folder browsed.

data.name: ChkConfirmOverwrite.ToolTip
data.value: One Word document is generated by walked folder, with name matching the folder name. If this mark is checked, any previously existing file is overwritten. If this mark is not checked, a user confirmation is requested before to overwrite a previously existing file.
